---

<div class="w-full py-8 px-4 md:px-48 mt-24 md:mt-48 border-t border-white/20">
      <div class="flex flex-col w-full items-center p-4">
            <div class="scale-90 opacity-90 flex flex-row items-center gap-4 font-thin border border-white/30 bg-white/5 w-fit px-1 md:px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
                  My Skills :>
            </div>
            <h2 class="w-full text-center mt-4 text-6xl font-bold">Engineering <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-accent from-purple-600 to-purple-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Capabilities</span></h2>
            <p class="max-w-154 text-center mt-4 text-base md:text-lg font-semibold opacity-75">I love exploring new technolgies! I believe honing my skills in new areas gives some insights on how each of them works and what makes them uniquely different from others</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 w-full flex flex-col gap-4 items-center">
            <div class="w-full md:hover:*:translate-x-8">
                  <div class="duration-250 p-8 flex flex-row gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/20">
                        <div class="h-full">
                              <div class="w-14 aspect-square rounded-2xl flex justify-center items-center text-xl font-thin bg-purple-700/5 border border-white/40">
                                    UX
                              </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-full flex flex-col">
                              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold">User Experience Layer</h3>
                              <p class="font-thin">The purpose of a website is to get visited by customers, and you don't want them to leave bad impression, right?</p>
                              <div class="mt-4  flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-4 *:border *:border-white *:py-1 *:px-4 *:rounded-xl">
                                    <span>Canva</span>
                                    <span>Figma</span>
                                    <span>TailwindCSS</span>
                                    <span>Motion.dev</span>
                                    <span>AnimeJS</span>
                              </div>
                        </div>
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:hover:*:translate-x-8">
                  <div class="duration-250 p-8 flex flex-row gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/20">
                        <div class="h-full">
                              <div class="w-14 aspect-square rounded-2xl flex justify-center items-center text-xl font-thin bg-purple-700/5 border border-white/40">
                                    API
                              </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-full flex flex-col">
                              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold">Application Logic Layer</h3>
                              <p class="font-thin">Of course, we have to use atleast basic API architecture in order to make the system secure and expectable</p>
                              <div class="mt-4  flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-4 *:border *:border-white *:py-1 *:px-4 *:rounded-xl">
                                    <span>Rust</span>
                                    <span>PHP</span>
                                    <span>Javascript</span>
                                    <span>Golang</span>
                                    <span>Python</span>
                                    <span>Dart</span>
                              </div>
                        </div>
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:hover:*:translate-x-8">
                  <div class="duration-250 p-8 flex flex-row gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/20">
                        <div class="h-full">
                              <div class="w-14 aspect-square rounded-2xl flex justify-center items-center text-xl font-thin bg-purple-700/5 border border-white/40">
                                    DB
                              </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-full flex flex-col">
                              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold">Storage Management Layer</h3>
                              <p class="font-thin">Data is one of the most important aspect regardless the industry. Data is precious!</p>
                              <div class="mt-4  flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-4 *:border *:border-white *:py-1 *:px-4 *:rounded-xl">
                                    <span>PostgreSQL</span>
                                    <span>MySQL</span>
                                    <span>SurrealDB</span>
                                    <span>MongoDB</span>
                                    <span>Redis</span>
                              </div>
                        </div>
                  </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:hover:*:translate-x-8">
                  <div class="duration-250 p-8 flex flex-row gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/20">
                        <div class="h-full">
                              <div class="w-14 aspect-square rounded-2xl flex justify-center items-center text-xl font-thin bg-purple-700/5 border border-white/40">
                                    OPS
                              </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-full flex flex-col">
                              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold">Development & Infrastructure Layer</h3>
                              <p class="font-thin">As the project gets bigger, It will be better to make it more reliable, and easy to develop, deploy and maintain</p>
                              <div class="mt-4  flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-4 *:border *:border-white *:py-1 *:px-4 *:rounded-xl">
                                    <span>Github</span>
                                    <span>Docker</span>
                                    <span>Kubernetes</span>
                                    <span>Cloudflare</span>
                              </div>
                        </div>
                  </div>
            </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 opacity-80 p-4 font-semibold text-center w-full border border-white/20 bg-purple-700/40 rounded-2xl">
            Every layer is designed to integrates with each other as one performant system- <span class="text-purple-300">not isolated, falling apart application :)</span>
      </div>
</div>